{"tid":304548,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【習總訪港】每週一字教「下半旗」 德領事有心定無意？","createTime":"2017-07-01T03:44:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-01T03:44:24.000Z","uid":39464,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0ac97a70bb29a0a6590302869fd6128c4e6702e3","tid":304548,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T03:44:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170701/large/1498877467_a3a0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170701%2Flarge%2F1498877467_a3a0.jpg&h=4c46b685&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 大批親共建制人士今日熱烈慶祝香港回歸20周年，今早更有升旗儀式。德國駐香港總領事館fb今早則更新「每週一字」，介紹「下半旗」、「哀傷」和「升旗方式」的德文，上載約半小時，已獲得超過500個「like」。<br />\n<br />\n德國駐香港總領事館fb指，下半旗的德文是「die Trauerbeflaggung」，「Trauer」解作哀傷，「beflaggung」則是升旗儀式。<br />\n<br />\n雖然「每週一字」的圖片背景是德國國旗下半旗及早前逝世的前德國總理科爾，但似乎不少香港網民都有共鳴，目前已獲得超過500個「like」及過百人分享。<br />\n<br />\n網民留言：<br />\nHambee Fan：黑色的幽默！真係代表咗大部分香港人的心聲！<br />\nPat Tiger：抽到水都乾<br />\nWang On：熱烈慶祝香港淪陷20周年！<br />\nRyan Chan：嘩。唔駛放科爾張相出嚟啦。明架啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170701/large/1498877485_93a5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170701%2Flarge%2F1498877485_93a5.jpg&h=6d1c644b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170701/56899896\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170701%2F56899896&d=O4NmLS%2FYfOScxcF7ZsI6K9ZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=15674958\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170701%2F56899896&h=39b9fe17\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170701/56899896</a>"}]}